    <note>Hu(1) Lin [7255] Su's [8064] father, Zonghui's [830], Zongyan's [832] and Zongyu's [833] grandfather, Yixiu's [818] great grandfather, Ge(2) Wu's [7264] father-in-law. The mother of another great grandson, Hu(1) Jiaoxiu [3395], was the daughter of Yao(1) Bi [4058] (a Zhenjiang, Jintan xian resident), whose grandson, Yao(1) Yu [4061], was appointed Sinong sicheng in 1194. Hu(1) Jiaoxiu's grandfather-in-law was Qian(1) Gongfu [147]. Hu Su, 40.12a (wife, born Li, who died in 1043 at age 75); Sun Di, Daquanji, 51.6b.</note>
